<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Izbira Entitete</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/izbiraEntitete.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway:400,300,600,800,900" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

    <div id="overlay">
        <div class="overlay-content">
            <div class="close-btn" onclick="closeOverlay()">
                <i class="material-icons">close</i>
            </div>
            <br>
            <h3>Navodila za uporabo</h3><br><br>
            <h4>1. Izbira med pari živali</h4>
            <p style="color: black">Prikazali se vam bodo pari entitet.
                V vsakem koraku izberite tisto sliko, s katero se najbolj poistovetite, s preprostim pritiskom.</p><br>
            <h4>2. Prekinitev samoocenitve</h4>
            <p style="color: black;">V kolikor želite prekiniti samoocenitev, to lahko storite kadarkoli pritiskom na
                gumb X.
                Vračanje nazaj ni dovoljeno.</p><br>
            <h4>3. Spremljanje napredka</h4>
            <p style="color: black;">Med samoocenjevanjem boste lahko spremljali svoj napredek.
                Prikazalo se bo, koliko izbir vas še čaka do zaključka.</p><br>
            <h4>4. Pregled samoocenitve:</h4>
            <p style="color: black;">Ko zaključite z izbiranjem, bo aplikacija samodejno prikazala "Pregled
                samoocenitve".
                V tem pregledu boste videli analizo in vaše pozitivne ter negativne plati.</p><br>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <br>
            <h3 style="color: white; font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #388E3C;">IZBERITE FOTOGRAFIJO</h3>
            <br>

            <div class="entities-container">
                <div class="entity-wrapper" data-index="0">
                    <p class="entity-name"><%= entities[0].naziv %></p>
                    <div id="entity1" class="entity">
                        <img src="<%= entities[0].slika %>" alt="<%= entities[0].naziv %>">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="arrow-wrapper">
                    <img id="arrow-left" class="arrow" src="/Animation/ArrowLeft.svg" alt="Arrow Left">
                    <img id="arrow-right" class="arrow" src="/Animation/ArrowRight.svg" alt="Arrow Right">
                </div>

                <div class="entity-wrapper" data-index="1">
                    <p class="entity-name"><%= entities[1].naziv %></p>
                    <div id="entity2" class="entity">
                        <img src="<%= entities[1].slika %>" alt="<%= entities[1].naziv %>">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <br><br>
            <div class="progress-bar-container">
                <div class="progress">
                    <div id="progress-bar" class="progress-bar" role="progressbar"></div>
                </div>
                <p id="progress-text">0/<%= entities.length %>
                </p>
            </div>

            <br>

            <div class="text-center mt-4" onclick="navigateTo('/samoocenitev');"
                onkeypress="navigateTo('/samoocenitev');" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Prekini samoocenitev"
                style="cursor: pointer;">
                <iframe src="https://lottie.host/embed/587828b4-39f0-473f-be62-970695bda6a2/dEPwmTqIyq.json"
                    frameborder="0" width="100" height="100" style="pointer-events: none;"></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const entities =  <%- JSON.stringify(entities) %>;

        function navigateTo(path) {
            window.location.href = path;
        }
    </script>
    <script>
        history.pushState(null, null, location.href);
        window.onpopstate = function () {
            history.go(1);
        };
    </script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/izbiraEntitete.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
